    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "The new mining block is created first(with executable transactions included), but the PoW fields are still unassigned. It's the unsealed block. Then it will be sent to the miners for finding the PoW solution in order to become a complete block.\r\n\r\nThe procedure of finding the correct PoW solution may take very long time(~13s)",
